od 1868 do 1892.

123
00:16:41,928 --> 00:16:45,261
Njegov sin Edvard je preuzeo posao,sve do 1925.

124
00:16:45,364 --> 00:16:47,696
Svi ugovori su pisani rukom.

125
00:16:47,833 --> 00:16:50,598
Moj deda, Charles;
moj otac, Henri.

126
00:16:50,704 --> 00:16:52,171
I ja.

127
00:16:52,306 --> 00:16:55,002
Da,dobro,to je to jer kao sto znas

128
00:16:55,142 --> 00:16:56,507
ja sam poslednji Lebel.

129
00:16:56,643 --> 00:16:59,043
Pokazacu ti testament coveka...

130
00:17:01,983 --> 00:17:03,813
... koji je imao nekoliko zivota.

131
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:08,019
Njegovi naslednici su otkrili

132
00:17:08,155 --> 00:17:09,985
da je imao tri zene u isto vreme.

133
00:17:10,122 --> 00:17:11,323
Jednu ovde, jednu u Majamiju,

134
00:17:11,325 --> 00:17:13,987
i jednu u Hondurasu,gde je imao posao.

135
00:17:15,395 --> 00:17:19,229
I tako... nisu vise troje dece naslednici.

136
00:17:19,366 --> 00:17:20,499
Vec osam.

137
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:22,696
To je sport, moj covek.

138
00:17:24,505 --> 00:17:26,370
Pogledaj. Hm!

139
00:17:28,408 --> 00:17:30,899
Smrt nikada nije kraj price.

140
00:17:31,044 --> 00:17:32,739
Uvek ostaju tragovi.

141
00:17:35,183 --> 00:17:36,912
Ako zelite da nadjete svog brata,

142
00:17:37,051 --> 00:17:39,485
onda cete morati da se vratite u proslost vase majke.

143
00:17:39,587 --> 00:17:42,181
- Jean, ja hocu da vratim svoju sestru,
to je sve.

144
00:17:42,323 --> 00:17:43,390
- To mi je jasno..

145
00:17:43,391 --> 00:17:45,587
Imam dva tri posla da zavrsim,

146
00:17:45,728 --> 00:17:47,195
tako da necu imati vremena.

147
00:17:47,363 --> 00:17:49,091
Tako,zavrsi svoje poslove,

148
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:50,492
pa bi trebali da krenemo...

149
00:17:50,598 --> 00:17:52,498
Moj pasos...

150
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:56,036
- "Mi"? Zar ne mislite da ste vec previse ucinili za nas?

151
00:17:56,170 --> 00:17:59,367
- Upravo tako,sad nije dobar trenutak da vas ostavim.

152
00:18:01,342 --> 00:18:03,037
Ja sam vas covek, Simon.

153
00:18:03,177 --> 00:18:05,372
Znam da sam vam potreban.

154
00:18:08,183 --> 00:18:09,775
- Mi cemo naci moju sestru,
i onda se vracamo.

155
00:18:09,918 --> 00:18:11,283
- Obecavam.

156
00:18:11,420 --> 00:18:13,445
Znate,
gospodine Marwan,obecanje

157
