158
00:21:12,739 --> 00:21:14,866
Sad pevaj.

159
00:22:21,676 --> 00:22:24,042
- Tiho,tiho.

160
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:27,545
Izlazi.

161
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:29,349
Vidim glavu.

162
00:22:29,518 --> 00:22:30,883
Guraj.

163
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:33,112
Guraj, devojko.

164
00:22:41,463 --> 00:22:43,055
Prva je izasla.

165
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:07,250
Sad odmori.

166
00:23:08,357 --> 00:23:09,722
Ponosna sam na tebe.

167
00:23:11,661 --> 00:23:13,686
Spremi se za drugu.

168
00:23:43,126 --> 00:23:44,389
Stani.

169
00:23:44,628 --> 00:23:45,959
Daj mi.

170
00:23:47,131 --> 00:23:48,331
- Sta to radis?

171
