206
00:25:38,579 --> 00:25:41,046
-Tako sam srecna sto si konacno samnom.

207
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:43,341
- I ja.

208
00:25:49,890 --> 00:25:51,858
- OK,to je ime medicinske sestre

209
00:25:52,025 --> 00:25:53,856
koja je pomogla mami da se porodi u zatvoru.

210
00:25:53,994 --> 00:25:55,553
