Chut, chut, chut.

240
00:31:03,585 --> 00:31:08,985
NIHAT

241
00:33:30,973 --> 00:33:33,636
- Vi ste stvarno poznavli Zenu Koja Peva?

242
00:33:33,776 --> 00:33:36,802
Vi ne znate kolko to meni znaci.

243
00:33:37,981 --> 00:33:39,949
- Nawal Marwan je radila za mene

244
00:33:40,049 --> 00:33:41,641
kao sekretarica 18 godina.

245
00:33:41,784 --> 00:33:44,014
Moja zena i ja,
mi smo obozavali

246
00:33:44,153 --> 00:33:45,644
nju i njenu decu.

247
00:33:46,657 --> 00:33:47,988
Ali priznajem da sam shvatio

248
00:33:48,158 --> 00:33:50,649
da je uopste nisam poznavao.

249
00:33:53,329 --> 00:33:55,491
Spremni?
- Spremni.

250
00:34:07,544 --> 00:34:09,034
- Hm...

251
00:34:10,681 --> 00:34:13,172
Gospodin Maddad je na moj zahtev istrazivao

252
00:34:13,350 --> 00:34:16,513
da bi pronasao tragove za vasim bratom i ocem.

253
00:34:22,026 --> 00:34:23,653
-Sto se tice oca,
Abu Tareka,

254
00:34:23,761 --> 00:34:26,525
jos nisam pronasao smrtovnicu.

255
00:34:26,697 --> 00:34:28,825
Drzava ga smatra nestalim.

256
00:34:28,933 --> 00:34:31,163
Mozda se odselio preko granice.

257
00:34:31,269 --> 00:34:34,568
To je ono sto se dogodilo sa takvim ljudima.

258
00:34:34,706 --> 00:34:36,105
Ili su mrtvi ili nestali.

259
00:34:36,241 --> 00:34:37,440
Moracete da vidite.

260
00:34:37,541 --> 00:34:39,703
- Mozda je i bolje tako.

261
00:34:40,745 --> 00:34:43,111
- Sto se tice brata...

262
00:34:43,248 --> 00:34:45,545
Vas klijent, Nawal Marwan,

263
00:34:45,682 --> 00:34:47,547
dolazi iz sela Der Om.

264
00:34:47,718 --> 00:34:51,951
Ona je urucila dete babici koja se zove Elham,

265
00:34:52,090 --> 00:34:55,890
koja je dete dala u sirotiste u Kfar Koutu

266
00:34:56,061 --> 00:34:58,393
maja 1970.

267
00:34:59,731 --> 00:35:02,599
Najveci deo posla je bio da se pronadju spisi.

268
00:35:02,735 --> 00:35:05,295
Mnogo dokumenata je izgubljeno u ratu.

269
00:35:06,305 --> 00:35:08,899
Ali ja sam pronasao spise

270
00:35:09,041 --> 00:35:11,304
koje su prepisane i donirane

271
00:35:11,443 --> 00:35:15,574
nacionalnoj arhivi od strane Sestara Milosrdja.

272
00:35:15,714 --> 00:35:19,410
U maju 1970, babica iz Der Oma, Elham,

273
00:35:19,584 --> 00:35:22,417
donela je na usvajanje musko dete.

274
00:35:22,555 --> 00:35:27,219
To je jedini decak doveden u sirotiste tog meseca.

275
00:35:27,326 --> 00:35:28,657
Vidite.

276
00:35:28,794 --> 00:35:31,957
Registrovan je pod imenom Nihat.

277
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:35,926
Datumi se poklapaju.

278
00:35:36,068 --> 00:35:37,558
To je on.

279
00:35:38,571 --> 00:35:41,734
- Ha! To je vas brat!Nihat!

280
00:35:45,278 --> 00:35:47,269
- Sirotiste u Kfar Khoutu,

281
00:35:47,414 --> 00:35:48,614
Nihat Maj.

282
00:35:48,615 --> 00:35:51,675
To je njegovo registrovano ime.

283
00:35:51,818 --> 00:35:53,018
Nihat iz maja meseca.

284
00:35:53,153 --> 00:35:55,587
Dali su mu privremeno prezime,

285
00:35:55,689 --> 00:35:57,020
ime meseca kad je dosao.

286
00:35:57,157 --> 00:36:00,183
U tom periodu nije bilo usvojenja.

287
00:36:00,327 --> 00:36:02,123
To je bio pocetak rata.

288
00:36:02,294 --> 00:36:05,024
Sirotiste je unisteno cetiri godine kasnije.

289
00:36:06,299 --> 00:36:08,961
Moramo da postavimo pitanje ko je unistio sirotiste u Kfar Khoutu

290
00:36:09,102 --> 00:36:11,969
da bi saznali sta se desilo sa decom.

291
00:36:13,974 --> 00:36:17,638
Izmedju nas,sa obzirom sta se desavalo u regionu...

292
00:36:18,646 --> 00:36:20,136
nema mnogo nade.

293
00:36:21,616 --> 00:36:23,641
- I on je najverovatnije mrtav.

294
00:36:23,784 --> 00:36:25,843
- Ne kazem da je mrtav

295
00:36:25,987 --> 00:36:28,114
Kazem da smo mu izgubili trag.

296
00:36:29,824 --> 00:36:31,655
- Mrtvi su obojica.

297
00:36:31,792 --> 00:36:34,225
Onda da otvorimo koverte,to je to.

298
00:36:34,361 --> 00:36:36,192
-To necu dozvoliti, Simon.

299
00:36:36,329 --> 00:36:38,160
Ovakve stvari su svetinja.

300
00:36:39,167 --> 00:36:41,829
On je pocinio silovanje.

301
00:36:42,003 --> 00:36:44,198
- Srecom,imam proslost.

302
00:36:46,908 --> 00:36:49,001
Izvinite.

303
00:36:50,646 --> 00:36:52,739
-I dalje imamo materijal za istrazivanje.

304
00:36:52,881 --> 00:36:56,145
Ali to je malo radikalno.

305
00:36:57,185 --> 00:36:58,251
Ratni zapovednik

306
00:36:58,252 --> 00:37:00,881
koji je unistio sirotiste jos je ziv.

307
00:37:01,023 --> 00:37:03,082
On bi mogao znati sta se desilo

308
00:37:03,225 --> 00:37:05,420
sa grupom dece gde je bio i Nihat.

309
00:37:05,561 --> 00:37:06,761
- Prosla je vecnost.

310
00:37:06,895 --> 00:37:08,556
- Morate razumeti

311
00:37:08,697 --> 00:37:11,895
da je taj period jedna serija odmazdi

312
00:37:12,035 --> 00:37:15,561
koje se medjusobno neumoljivo logicno uklapaju,

313
00:37:15,704 --> 00:37:17,194
cak dopunjuju jedna drugu.

314
00:37:19,540 --> 00:37:21,508
Vojni zapovednici su upravo ona vrsta ljudi

315
00:37:21,609 --> 00:37:23,771
Koji imaju dobro pamcenje.

316
00:37:23,912 --> 00:37:26,244
I on se seca,verujte mi.

317
00:37:27,683 --> 00:37:29,514
Wallat Chamseddine,

318
00:37:29,618 --> 00:37:31,051
to mu je ime.

319
00:37:35,358 --> 00:37:36,723
- Jel se zna gde je?

320
00:37:36,859 --> 00:37:39,851
- Zna se.
Pronadje on tebe.

321
00:37:42,732 --> 00:37:44,757
Ali mozemo nesto da pokusamo.

322
00:37:46,603 --> 00:37:49,265
Da li volite caj,gospodine Marwan?

323
00:37:53,275 --> 00:37:55,243
- Red je na tebe.

324
00:37:58,715 --> 00:38:00,444
Ides da posetis

325
00:38:00,583 --> 00:38:02,574
Izbeglicki kamp u Deressi.

326
00:38:02,752 --> 00:38:04,219
Ti ces popiti caj

327
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,582
bilo gde u kampu

328
00:38:05,755 --> 00:38:07,621
sa onim ko te pozove na caj.

329
00:38:07,758 --> 00:38:10,749
Ti onda kazi da si sin Zene Koja Peva

330
00:38:10,893 --> 00:38:12,758
i da trazis Nihata Maja.

331
00:38:12,929 --> 00:38:15,056
Ne mozes tamo ici sam

332
00:38:16,332 --> 00:38:18,426
Naci cu nekoga

333
00:38:18,569 --> 00:38:20,093
da ide sa tobom

334
00:38:42,192 --> 00:38:43,955
-Dobrodosli u Deressu.

335
00:39:52,531 --> 00:39:54,361
- Ha! Ha!
Jel znas gde ides, Simon?

336
00:39:54,532 --> 00:39:55,932
- Znam.

337
00:40:22,295 --> 00:40:23,523
Kako ste?

338
00:40:24,865 --> 00:40:26,355
- Tako ti boga, ala si porastao!

339
00:40:26,532 --> 00:40:29,297
-Zavrsio sam inzinjerske studije.

340
00:40:29,469 --> 00:40:34,099
Nisam nasao posao,
i zato vozim taxi.

341
00:40:34,274 --> 00:40:36,299
- Otkud ti ovde?

342
00:40:36,476 --> 00:40:41,540
- Tu sam sa strancima,
koji su me zamolili da ih dovezem ovde.

343
00:40:43,418 --> 00:40:45,283
-Dobrodosli,dodjite.

344
00:40:45,453 --> 00:40:47,784
- Ne,hvala,zurimo.

345
00:40:47,954 --> 00:40:49,785
- Molim vas,dodji te.

346
00:40:55,096 --> 00:40:57,826
-Poziva nas na caj.

347
00:40:57,965 --> 00:40:59,165
- Ah, dobro!

348
00:41:16,317 --> 00:41:20,151
- Uh,pita se zasto ste dosli u Deressu.

349
00:41:23,292 --> 00:41:25,783
- Trazim nekog ko se zove Nihat Maj.

350
00:41:35,138 --> 00:41:38,129
-On ne poznaje Nihata Maja.

351
00:41:38,273 --> 00:41:41,470
Pitao je kako se ti zoves.

352
00:41:48,817 --> 00:41:51,650
- Moja majka je rodom iz sela
Der Om, na Jugu.

353
00:42:04,900 --> 00:42:06,994
Moja majka je Zena Koja Peva.

354
00:42:32,395 --> 00:42:34,488
Da,to je uredu.Uradjeno.

355
00:42:39,670 --> 00:42:41,228
Da cekamo sta?

356
00:43:14,573 --> 00:43:16,541
- Sarwan Marwan?-Da.

357
00:43:16,641 --> 00:43:18,973
- Dosli smo da vam ponudimo pomoc.

358
00:43:19,110 --> 00:43:21,407
Vraticete se za sat vremana.

359
00:43:22,647 --> 00:43:24,137
- Da li mogu da javim sestri?

360
00:43:24,282 --> 00:43:27,308
- Ne,vracate se za jedan sat,obecavam.

361
00:43:28,787 --> 00:43:31,255
- Samo da obucem drugu kosulju.

362
00:43:34,060 --> 00:43:35,260
- Telefonirace.

363
00:43:35,628 --> 00:43:36,993
- Bice sve uredu

364
00:43:37,663 --> 00:43:40,496
- Vec! Nemojte da brinete,sve je uredu.

365
00:43:40,632 --> 00:43:44,068
Ah, jel sam vam rekao: Jug,
bacite varnicu i onda sve eksplodira.

366
00:43:44,269 --> 00:43:45,669
Oh, u redu.

367
00:44:59,913 --> 00:45:03,179
Ti si nam bila od velike koristi,
sad je red na nas da mi tebi pomognemo.

368
00:45:04,552 --> 00:45:06,075
Vi cete napustiti zemlju.

369
00:45:06,253 --> 00:45:07,982
Tako je lakse.

370
00:45:08,155 --> 00:45:10,589
Naci cemo vam kucu i posao.

371
00:45:11,525 --> 00:45:14,518
Zelim da imate bolji zivot.

372
00:45:16,330 --> 00:45:19,094
Mi imamo dosta kontakta u Americi.

373
00:45:20,902 --> 00:45:23,098
Vi morate otici sa svojom decom.

374
00:45:23,706 --> 00:45:26,539
Znate da su ziva.Neka krenu sa vama.

375
00:45:29,712 --> 00:45:33,374
Deca ce vam pomoci,videcete.

376
00:45:40,188 --> 00:45:43,123
- Ne mozete to da trazite od mene.

377
00:45:44,960 --> 00:45:47,258
- Vasa deca su i nasa deca, Nawal.

378
00:45:47,429 --> 00:45:49,556
Vasa porodica je i nasa porodica.

379
00:45:50,065 --> 00:45:51,265
Verujte mi.

380
00:45:52,701 --> 00:45:55,637
Ja cu vam pomoci

381
00:45:55,805 --> 00:45:59,137
Ja cu uvek biti tu za vas i vasu decu.

382
00:46:01,138 --> 00:46:06,138
CHAMSEDDINE

383
00:46:48,658 --> 00:46:50,149
Dobar dan, Sarwan.

384
00:46:52,296 --> 00:46:55,958
Izvinite zbog ovakvog dovodjenja,ali to je radi vase sigurnosti.

385
00:46:58,134 --> 00:47:01,036
Ja se zovem Wallat Chamseddine.

386
00:47:03,440 --> 00:47:07,774
Kazite mi, sta mogu da uradim da bih vam pomogao, Sarwan Marwan?

387
00:47:09,513 --> 00:47:11,276
- Poznavali ste moju majku.

388
00:47:11,382 --> 00:47:14,011
- Da kazemo da je radila za mene

389
00:47:14,151 --> 00:47:17,177
Sta mogu da uradim da bih pomogao?

390
00:47:21,158 --> 00:47:24,492
- Trazim coveka koji se zove Nihat Maj.

391
00:47:25,530 --> 00:47:27,657
-Zasto trazite Nihata Maja?

392
00:47:29,668 --> 00:47:30,868
- On je moj brat.

393
00:47:30,869 --> 00:47:33,360
Moja majka mi je rekla da ga pronadjem.

394
00:47:35,073 --> 00:47:36,904
- A otkud znate da je

395
00:47:37,042 --> 00:47:40,067
Nihat Maj sin Nawal Marwan?

396
00:47:42,847 --> 00:47:44,645
- Moj brat je dat na usvajanje

397
00:47:44,749 --> 00:47:46,512
u sirotiste Kfar Khout.

398
00:47:47,853 --> 00:47:50,822
Nasli smo registar sa originalnim podacima.

399
00:47:51,823 --> 00:47:53,484
Datumi... Sve se uklapa.

400
00:47:53,592 --> 00:47:55,823
Nihat Maj je moj brat.

401
00:48:39,071 --> 00:48:41,131
- Ja i moji prijatelji smo napali

402
00:48:41,275 --> 00:48:43,607
hriscansko selo Kfar Khout...

403
00:48:44,611 --> 00:48:46,078
To je bio odgovor na agresiju

404
00:48:46,246 --> 00:48:49,079
gde su nasa braca,izbeglice,bili zrtve.

405
00:48:50,718 --> 00:48:53,811
Dosli smo u sirotiste Kfar Khout.

406
00:48:54,888 --> 00:48:56,947
Spasili smo decu.

407
00:48:57,090 --> 00:48:59,216
Poveo sam ih sa nama.

408
00:48:59,325 --> 00:49:02,227
I Nihat je bio medju njima.

409
00:49:02,329 --> 00:49:04,263
Obucavali smo ih i pripremali

410
00:49:04,431 --> 00:49:06,626
da se bore za nas.

411
00:49:07,834 --> 00:49:10,098
Nihat, on je imao dar.

412
00:49:10,270 --> 00:49:12,762
Bio je deo nas.

413
00:49:12,941 --> 00:49:16,104
I uskoro je postao zastrasujuci snajperista.

414
00:49:17,412 --> 00:49:21,940
Ali on je zeleo da pronadje svoju majku.

415
00:49:22,116 --> 00:49:24,084
Trazio ju je mesecima.

416
00:49:25,520 --> 00:49:28,785
Nihat,ja ne znam sta je on video ili cuo.

417
00:49:29,791 --> 00:49:31,280
On je postao...

418
00:49:32,459 --> 00:49:34,792
ludak rata.

419
00:49:34,963 --> 00:49:38,865
Dosao je da me vidi,i zatrazio da bude mucenik

420
00:49:39,000 --> 00:49:41,468
da bi njegova majka mogla da vidi njegovu sliku

421
00:49:41,636 --> 00:49:42,933
svuda,na zidovima sirom zemlje.

422
00:49:44,172 --> 00:49:45,800
Ali ja sam ga odbio.

423
00:49:47,710 --> 00:49:49,700
Vratio se u Daresh.

424
00:49:50,778 --> 00:49:52,939
Postao je slobodni strelac,

425
00:49:53,047 --> 00:49:55,311
najopasniji u celom regionu.

426
00:49:55,484 --> 00:49:56,684
Prava masina.

427
00:49:56,819 --> 00:49:58,684
Pucao je u svakog.

428
00:49:58,821 --> 00:50:03,224
I onda,
bila je neprijateljska invazija.

429
00:50:04,626 --> 00:50:06,116
I jednog jutra...

430
00:50:07,130 --> 00:50:09,063
Zarobili su Nihata.

431
00:50:09,198 --> 00:50:10,995
Ubio je sedam snajperista.

432
00:50:13,068 --> 00:50:14,831
Nisu ga ubili.

433
00:50:14,970 --> 00:50:16,334
Obucili su ga

434
00:50:16,471 --> 00:50:19,168
i poslali u zatvor Kfar Ryat.

435
00:50:20,542 --> 00:50:22,237
- On je bio u zatvoru?

436
00:50:22,378 --> 00:50:23,845
- Da.

437
00:50:26,215 --> 00:50:27,648
Kao dzelat.

438
00:50:29,819 --> 00:50:31,719
- On je radio sa mojim ocem?

439
00:50:31,855 --> 00:50:33,823
- Ne,on nije radio

440
00:50:33,923 --> 00:50:35,857
sa Abu Tareko,tvojim ocem.

441
00:51:04,889 --> 00:51:06,356
- Jel si dobro?

442
00:51:11,027 --> 00:51:12,518
- 1 plus 1...

443
00:51:13,531 --> 00:51:15,396
je dva.

444
00:51:15,533 --> 00:51:17,023
- Sta?

445
00:51:20,071 --> 00:51:22,130
-1 plus 1 jednako 2.

446
00:51:23,141 --> 00:51:24,631
To ne moze biti 1.

447
00:51:31,248 --> 00:51:33,044
- Hej, ti imas groznicu.

448
00:51:35,453 --> 00:51:36,943
- Jeanne?

449
00:51:38,823 --> 00:51:41,451
1 plus 1,
da li moze da bude 1?

450
00:52:03,115 --> 00:52:04,980
- Tamo ima praznih mesta.

451
00:52:05,117 --> 00:52:06,448
- Oh, idi ako zelis.

452
00:53:35,243 --> 00:53:37,609
-Mozemo li vam pomoci,
gospodjo?

453
00:53:45,753 --> 00:53:47,721
- Izvinite.

454
00:54:58,094 --> 00:55:00,459
(W. Chamseddine ):
Postavsi dzelat,

455
00:55:00,596 --> 00:55:03,088
tvoj brat je promenio ime.

456
00:55:03,199 --> 00:55:05,759
On je postao Abu Tarek.

457
00:55:08,672 --> 00:55:11,641
Nihat Maj je Abu Tarek.

458
00:55:15,880 --> 00:55:18,348
Mi znamo da sada zivi u Kanadi

459
00:55:18,482 --> 00:55:20,506
pod novim identitetom.

460
00:55:20,650 --> 00:55:23,142
Nihat Harmanni.

461
00:56:01,659 --> 00:56:03,149
- Gospodine Harmanni?

462
00:56:06,397 --> 00:56:07,531
- Da?

463
00:56:14,873 --> 00:56:16,363
-Ovo je za vas.

464
00:57:02,389 --> 00:57:05,085
<i>Pisem a sva drhtim.</i>

465
00:57:05,259 --> 00:57:06,817
<i>Ja sam tebe prepoznala.</i>

466
00:57:06,960 --> 00:57:09,587
<i>Ti mene nisi prepoznao.</i>

467
00:57:09,762 --> 00:57:11,627
<i>To je neverovatno cudo.</i>

468
00:57:11,764 --> 00:57:13,426
<i>Ja sam tvoj broj 72.</i>

469
00:57:13,567 --> 00:57:17,832
<i>Ovo pismo ce ti biti uruceno od strane nase dece.</i>

470
00:57:17,970 --> 00:57:19,961
<i>ti ih neces prepoznati</i>

471
00:57:20,106 --> 00:57:21,937
<i>zato sto su predivni,</i>

472
00:57:22,108 --> 00:57:24,441
<i>ali oni znaju ko si ti.</i>

473
00:57:33,120 --> 00:57:35,350
<i>Preko njih, zelim da ti kazem</i>

474
00:57:35,489 --> 00:57:37,457
<i>da si jos uvek ziv.</i>

475
00:57:37,624 --> 00:57:39,615
<i>Ali uskoro ces ucutati.</i>

476
00:57:39,793 --> 00:57:41,283
<i>Znam.</i>

477
00:57:42,629 --> 00:57:45,292
<i>Jer tisina je za sve one koji se suoce sa istinom.</i>

478
00:57:46,301 --> 00:57:49,361
<i>Potpis.: kurva 72.</i>

479
00:58:03,016 --> 00:58:05,678
<i>Govorim sinu.</i>

480
00:58:05,819 --> 00:58:07,845
